#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Intangiriro"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Welcome to &kate;, a programmer's text editor by &kde;. Some of &kate;'s "
"many features include configurable syntax highlighting for languages ranging "
"from C and C++ to &HTML; to bash scripts, the ability to create and maintain "
"projects, a multiple document interface (<acronym>MDI</acronym>), and a self-"
"contained terminal emulator."
msgstr ""
"Kuri &kate; , A Umwandiko Muhinduzi ya:  &kde; Verisiyo 2 . 2 na hejuru . "
"Bya &kate; ' S Ibiranga Gushyiramo Igaragaza cyane ya:  Indimi Kuva: na + + "
"Kuri <acronym> </acronym> Kuri Inyandikoporogaramu , i Kuri Kurema na "
"Imishinga , A Igikubo Inyandiko Imigaragarire ( <acronym> </acronym> ) , na "
"A - Bihera . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"But &kate; is more than a programmer's editor. Its ability to open several "
"files at once makes it ideal for editing &UNIX;'s many configuration files. "
"This document was written in &kate;."
msgstr ""
"&kate; ni Birenzeho A Muhinduzi . Kuri Gufungura Idosiye Ku Rimwe ya:  "
"Guhindura &UNIX; ' S Iboneza Idosiye . Inyandiko in &kate; . "

